<div id="page-index">
  <div class="intro"></div>

  <p>Welcome to the WebKit bug reporting and tracking system.</p>

  <p>Choose from the following options:</p>
  <ul>
    <li id="query"><a href="query.cgi">Search existing [% terms.bug %] reports</a></li>
